short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Your personal help with Terms of Service and Privacy

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A website's Terms of Service is often challenging to comprehend and take too much time to read, so no one thoroughly checks them. In this way, the system isn't suitable for informing and creating awareness among the users. 

Obelize presents the Terms of Service in a new accessible way; easily understandable, concise, and trustworthy information but still integrable in your workflow. The design informs users with data of the Terms of Service; Didn't Read community, offers legal privacy-protecting settings, and advises people to understand the consequences of the website's policy and personal privacy settings.

Obelize will inform users about their data use as the aim of the GDPR established. The goal of the GDPR to inform users before they make a considered decision can become a reality with Obelize for the first time.
